These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, classical
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, british
1. the british is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes blood-red is the fan of electronic##1
4. the british is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre      | electronic  | classical   |
| Color   | blood-red     | yellow   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Nationality     | brazilian | british    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
House: tower, cape-cod
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, puzzles
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person playing bridge##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| House          | tower     | cape-cod |
| Hobby   | puzzles | photography  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Game     | monopoly   | bridge    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different games are played: go, scrabble
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Flower    | lily     | balloon-flower |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Game         | go         | scrabble        |
| Hobby   | reading         | sudoku    |

 #################################

 
