.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, sudoku
2 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg
City: liverpool, berlin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person playing poker##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Hobby           | sudoku | traveling    |
| Game   | poker       | mah-jongg |
| City           | liverpool         | berlin    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

