The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, pop
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, ivory
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre    | martial-arts | epic    |
| Music-Genre         | pop        | dubstep |
| Color         | blue          | ivory     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 